high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the counter top on your right.
Pick up egg from the counter top.
Turn around and walk to the microwave to your left.
Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the counter top.
Place egg on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Heating egg and placing it on kitchen

high_descs: Head through the door and turn right towards the countertop.
Take the egg from the kitchen countertop.
Turn around and move towards the microwave.
Open the oven, place the egg inside for some time to cook and take the egg out and close the oven.
Turn around and move towards the countertop.
Place the egg on the countertop in front of the oven.
anns.task_desc: Cook the egg and put it on the countertop in front of the oven.

high_descs: Turn Left, leave the room, turn right and walk towards the countertop.
Pick the egg from the table.
Open the microwave, put the egg inside and close the microwave, wait then open the microwave and get back the egg.
Turn right and then turn left and look in the countertop.
Put the egg on the countertop in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To heat the Egg on the CounterTop.
